snippet.title: The League of Explorers Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description: Adventure awaits!  Join the League of Explorers and set off on an expedition with your new friends to reclaim an ancient artifact of immense power! Discover powerful new cards for your Hearthstone decks! Visit www.TheLeagueofExplorers.com to learn more!
